OL,3,CThree sentenced for making 'Breaking
OL,4,CBad-style' meth labs in the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FThree men have been sentenced for
OL,8,Ftheir involvement in the production of
OL,9,FBreaking Bad-style crystal meth in
OL,10,Flabs across the West Midlands.
OL,12,FBetween 2020 and 2024, Jan Lacko, 49,
OL,13,FDavid Sivak, 44, and Mohammed Akhtar,
OL,14,F45, ran multiple makeshift 'kitchen
OL,15,Flaboratories' in residential
OL,16,Fproperties.
OL,18,FWest Midlands Police said they would
OL,19,Fuse chemistry instruments as well as
OL,20,Fdangerous chemicals to "cook" the meth.
