OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FThe gang would refer to the drug as
OL,8,F'pervitin' or 'piko' ` which are known
OL,9,Fto be slang terms for the highly-
OL,10,Faddictive drug.
OL,12,FAfter initially giving not-guilty
OL,13,Fpleas, the trio admitted to running
OL,14,Fthe production of methylamphetamine a
OL,15,FClass A controlled drug, in May this
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FEach man has now been sentenced for
OL,19,Ftheir part in the illegal operation.
OL,21,F'Highly addictive'
