OL,7,FSgt Antony Draper, from Birmingham's
OL,8,Fserious organised crime and
OL,9,Fexploitation team, said: "Crystal meth
OL,10,Fhas grown large exposure in the public
OL,11,Fthrough entertainment, and more
OL,12,Fspecifically US television drama,
OL,13,FBreaking Bad.
OL,15,F"However, the reality of this highly
OL,16,Faddictive and dangerous drug, is far
OL,17,Ffrom glamorous. It is much dirtier,
OL,18,Fand comes with serious health
OL,19,Fimplications for users.
