OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,F"It is highly addictive and takes a
OL,8,Fhuge toll on the human body.
OL,10,F"The production of the drug is also
OL,11,Fhighly dangerous, creating a
OL,12,Fsubstantial risk to all those around.
OL,14,F"With highly dangerous chemicals
OL,15,Finvolved, the risks of serious injury
OL,16,Fare incredibly high, due to the large
OL,17,Famount of toxic waste produced, as
OL,18,Fwell as toxic fumes ` all which create
OL,19,Fa dangerous risk of fires and
OL,20,Fexplosions."
