OL,7,F"This was a complex investigation that
OL,8,Frequired specialist support from CBRN
OL,9,Ftrained officers to assist with the
OL,10,Fexecution of warrants, scientific and
OL,11,Fforensic support, translation
OL,12,Fservices, shipping data and mobile
OL,13,Fphone analysis."
OL,15,FThe investigation
OL,17,FOfficers from the Birmingham Serious
OL,18,FOrganised Crime and Exploitation Team
OL,19,F(Socex), began investigating. Evidence
OL,20,Fwas collated following multiple
OL,21,Fwarrants, and vehicle stops.
