OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FAkhtar was found to act as the
OL,8,Fprocurer of the required chemicals and
OL,9,Fthe bulk delivery of required
OL,10,Fpseudoephedrine containing medication,
OL,11,Ffrom various overseas pharmaceutical
OL,12,Fcompanies, to Sivak and Lacko.
OL,14,FLacko and Akhtar were both arrested
OL,15,Fand charged in November 2024, while
OL,16,FSivak was arrested and charged in
OL,17,FJanuary earlier this year.
OL,19,FWhat happened to the trio?
