OL,3,CThree sentenced for making 'Breaking
OL,4,CBad-style' meth labs in the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FThe trio all pleaded guilty to being
OL,8,Fconcerned in the production of
OL,9,Fmethylamphetamine a Class A controlled
OL,10,Fdrug, at Birmingham Crown Court on
OL,11,FTuesday (13 May). Lacko also pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to supplying a controlled drug
OL,13,Fof Class A ` methylamphetamine.
OL,15,FLacko, of Grove Lane, Birmingham, was
OL,16,Fjailed for three years and seven
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,19,FSivak, of no fixed address, was jailed
OL,20,Ffor two years and four months.
